query:
SELECT id as "id!: i32", 
campaign_id as "campaign_id!: i32", 
advertiser_id as "advertiser_id!: String", 
member_id as "member_id!: String", 
collab_trigger_unique_id as "collab_trigger_unique_id!: String", 
handle_id as "handle_id!: i32", 
status as "status!: CollabStatus", 
dispute_reason as "dispute_reason!: Option < String >", 
reward as "reward!: String", 
fee as "fee!: Option < String >", 
created_at as "created_at!: UtcDateTime" FROM collabs WHERE (NOT $1::boolean OR id = $2::int4) AND (NOT $3::boolean OR id = ANY(CAST($4 as int4[])) ) AND (NOT $5::boolean OR campaign_id = $6::int4) AND (NOT $7::boolean OR campaign_id = ANY(CAST($8 as int4[])) ) AND (NOT $9::boolean OR advertiser_id = $10::varchar) AND (NOT $11::boolean OR advertiser_id = ANY(CAST($12 as varchar[])) ) AND (NOT $13::boolean OR member_id = $14::varchar) AND (NOT $15::boolean OR member_id = ANY(CAST($16 as varchar[])) ) AND (NOT $17::boolean OR collab_trigger_unique_id = $18::varchar) AND (NOT $19::boolean OR handle_id = $20::int4) AND (NOT $21::boolean OR handle_id = ANY(CAST($22 as int4[])) ) AND (NOT $23::boolean OR status = $24::collab_status) AND (NOT $25::boolean OR dispute_reason = $26::varchar) AND (NOT $27::boolean OR reward = $28::varchar) AND (NOT $29::boolean OR fee = $30::varchar) AND (NOT $31::boolean OR created_at = $32::timestamptz) ORDER BY 
      (CASE ($33 = 'Id' AND NOT $34) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($33 = 'Id' AND $34) WHEN true THEN id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($33 = 'CampaignId' AND NOT $34) WHEN true THEN campaign_id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($33 = 'CampaignId' AND $34) WHEN true THEN campaign_id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($33 = 'AdvertiserId' AND NOT $34) WHEN true THEN advertiser_id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($33 = 'AdvertiserId' AND $34) WHEN true THEN advertiser_id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($33 = 'MemberId' AND NOT $34) WHEN true THEN member_id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($33 = 'MemberId' AND $34) WHEN true THEN member_id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($33 = 'CollabTriggerUniqueId' AND NOT $34) WHEN true THEN collab_trigger_unique_id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($33 = 'CollabTriggerUniqueId' AND $34) WHEN true THEN collab_trigger_unique_id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($33 = 'HandleId' AND NOT $34) WHEN true THEN handle_id ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($33 = 'HandleId' AND $34) WHEN true THEN handle_id ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($33 = 'Status' AND NOT $34) WHEN true THEN status ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($33 = 'Status' AND $34) WHEN true THEN status ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($33 = 'DisputeReason' AND NOT $34) WHEN true THEN dispute_reason ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($33 = 'DisputeReason' AND $34) WHEN true THEN dispute_reason ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($33 = 'Reward' AND NOT $34) WHEN true THEN reward ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($33 = 'Reward' AND $34) WHEN true THEN reward ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($33 = 'Fee' AND NOT $34) WHEN true THEN fee ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($33 = 'Fee' AND $34) WHEN true THEN fee ELSE NULL END) DESC
    ,
      (CASE ($33 = 'CreatedAt' AND NOT $34) WHEN true THEN created_at ELSE NULL END),
      (CASE ($33 = 'CreatedAt' AND $34) WHEN true THEN created_at ELSE NULL END) DESC
     LIMIT $35 OFFSET $36
